# ------------ System Parameters ------------ #
1.2     # 0 eta: Dimensionless constant specifying the smoothing length
1.667   # 1 gamma: Heat capacity ratio
3       # 2 d: Number of spatial dimensions
0.0     # 3 x0: Bottom left corner  (x-coordinate)
0.0     # 4 y0: Bottom left corner  (y-coordinate)
0.0     # 5 z0: Bottom left corner  (z-coordinate)
1.0     # 6 wd: Width of the system's domain
0.75    # 7 lg: Length of the system's domain
0.75    # 8 hg: Height of the system's domain
1.0     # 9 rhol: Initial left density
0.125   # 10 rhor: Initial right density
1.0     # 11 Pl: Left initial pressure
0.1     # 12 Pr: Right initial pressure
0.5     # 13 xm: Discontinuity position

# ---------- Simulation Parameters ---------- #
0.0     # 14 t0: Initial time
0.2     # 15 tf: Final time
0.0001  # 16 dt: Initial time step
10      # 17 it_save: Frequency of data saving
128      # 18 nxl: Particle resolution in the x direction (left)
64      # 19 nxr: Particle resolution in the x direction (right)
24      # 20 nyl: Particle resolution in the y direction (left)
12      # 21 nyr: Particle resolution in the y direction (right)
24      # 22 nzl: Particle resolution in the z direction (left)
12      # 23 nzr: Particle resolution in the z direction (right)

# ------------- Tree parameters ------------- #
10      # 24 s: Maximum number of particles in a leaf (Bucket size)
0.5     # 25 alpha: Fraction of the bucket size s
0.5     # 26 Maximum ratio of cells with less than alpha*s particles